ns/transformers/links.ts","target":"https://github.com/aarnphm/aarnphm.github.io/blob/41a2f0d23e7d7432d24ecf603e2ffe5a1fccaa12/quartz/plugins/transformers/links.ts","line":969},{"title":"TurnTrout.com/quartz/plugins/transformers/linkfavicons.ts","target":"https://github.com/alexander-turner/TurnTrout.com/blob/56b56698937765b35f7156535bf664b905bda526/quartz/plugins/transformers/linkfavicons.ts#L171","line":973},{"title":"catcodeme version","target":"https://github.com/CatCodeMe/catcodeme.github.io/blob/770f3f8d1f6849ef40bc06b4300a52b3aecfb551/quartz/styles/external-links.scss","line":974},{"title":"Image sources and attributions","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/meta/Image-sources-and-attributions","line":1008},{"title":"hobbies | Eilleen’s e-Notebook![apex","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/static/profile_pic_2025.png","line":1014},{"title":"Upgrading to quartz 4.4","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/tbd/Upgrading-to-quartz-4.4","line":1120},{"title":"Robots.txt template - allowlist | DITig","target":"https://www.ditig.com/publications/robots-txt-template","line":1184},{"title":"Link to original","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/meta/About-robots.txt-and-crawlers#template-used","line":1192},{"title":"Permalinks tracker","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/meta/Permalinks-tracker","line":1271},{"title":"fanteastick/quartz-test@6c4a8af · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/fanteastick/quartz-test/commit/6c4a8afb76672af7909a7b675651420138c01fbd","line":1389},{"title":"GitHub - Naraenda/quartz-ascone","target":"https://github.com/Naraenda/quartz-ascone","line":1389},{"title":"fanteastick/quartz-test@a24b5b5 · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/fanteastick/quartz-test/commit/a24b5b57a24b2ce78dcf53867e597a9c14fff8bd","line":1399},{"title":"Add a page title suffix config option · ripdrive/ripdrive.github.io@db514fd · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/ripdrive/ripdrive.github.io/commit/db514fd4ae441f203069ae9e8e9b2ee5591d63c5","line":1531},{"title":"Link to original","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/meta/Hiding-tags-from-various-components#summary","line":1595},{"title":"RandomPageButton.tsx","target":"https://github.com/t-schreibs/sound-accumulator/blob/497adf732f8260e0f936a6a4cb9d619febf6bef1/quartz/components/RandomPageButton.tsx","line":1681},{"title":"randomPage.scss","target":"https://github.com/t-schreibs/sound-accumulator/blob/497adf732f8260e0f936a6a4cb9d619febf6bef1/quartz/components/styles/randomPage.scss","line":1682},{"title":"randomPage.inline.ts","target":"https://github.com/t-schreibs/sound-accumulator/blob/497adf732f8260e0f936a6a4cb9d619febf6bef1/quartz/components/scripts/randomPage.inline.ts","line":1683},{"title":"morrowind-modding/morrowind-modding.github.io@1bad00e · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/morrowind-modding/morrowind-modding.github.io/commit/1bad00e1e8b27ee2dc85ab08dd2da5b75642f5b3","line":1691},{"title":"GitHub secrets","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/tbd/GitHub-secrets#secrets-specifically-for-quartz","line":1693},{"title":"t-schreibs · sound-accumulator · OnlyFor.tsx · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/t-schreibs/sound-accumulator/blob/main/quartz%2Fcomponents%2FOnlyFor.tsx","line":1764},{"title":"\n\tawait write({\n\t  ctx,\n\t  content: pageContent,\n\t  slug,\n\t  ext: \".html\",\n\t}),\n```\n\nIn the scss, make a new section for `.page#quartz-404-body` and remove all the mobile styling for somethings, set the sidebar height to 0, merge some stuff for `@media all and ($tablet), @media all and ($mobile)`:\n\n> base.scss\n> \n> ```\n> .page {\n>   // This will give special grid styling to the 404 page, which is just skipping the tablet layout\n>   // because it looked weird when there was nothing in the left sidebar\n>   & > #quartz-404-body {\n>     display: grid;\n>     grid-template-columns: #{map.get($desktopGrid, templateColumns)};\n>     grid-template-rows: #{map.get($desktopGrid, templateRows)};\n>     column-gap: #{map.get($desktopGrid, columnGap)};\n>     row-gap: #{map.get($desktopGrid, rowGap)};\n>     grid-template-areas: #{map.get($desktopGrid, templateAreas)};\n>  \n>     @media all and ($tablet), all and ($mobile) {\n>       grid-template-columns: #{map.get($mobileGrid, templateColumns)};\n>       grid-template-rows: #{map.get($mobileGrid, templateRows)};\n>       column-gap: #{map.get($mobileGrid, columnGap)};\n>       row-gap: #{map.get($mobileGrid, rowGap)};\n>       grid-template-areas: #{map.get($mobileGrid, templateAreas)};\n>     }\n>  \n>     // Remove or adjust other styles as needed\n>     padding: 0 1rem;\n>     margin-right: 10px;\n>   \n>     & .sidebar {\n>       gap: 2rem;\n>       top: 0;\n>       box-sizing: border-box;\n>       padding: $topSpacing 2rem 2rem 2rem;\n>       display: flex;\n>       height: 0vh;\n>       position: sticky;\n>     }\n>   \n>     & .sidebar.left {\n>       z-index: 1;\n>       grid-area: grid-sidebar-left;\n>       flex-direction: column;\n>       @media all and ($tablet), all and ($mobile) {\n>         gap: 0;\n>         align-items: center;\n>         position: initial;\n>         display: flex;\n>         // height: unset;\n>         flex-direction: row;\n>         padding: 0;\n>         padding-top: 2rem;\n>       }\n>     }\n>   \n>     & .sidebar.right {\n>       grid-area: grid-sidebar-right;\n>       margin-right: 0;\n>       flex-direction: column;\n>     }\n>   \n>     & .page-header,\n>     & .page-footer {\n>       margin-top: 1rem;\n>       @media all and ($tablet), all and ($mobile) {\n>         display: none;\n>       }\n>     }\n>   \n>     & .page-header {\n>       grid-area: grid-header;\n>       margin: $topSpacing 0 0 0;\n>     }\n>   \n>     & .center > article {\n>       grid-area: grid-center;\n>     }\n>   \n>     & footer {\n>       grid-area: grid-footer;\n>     }\n>   \n>     & .center,\n>     & footer {\n>       max-width: 100%;\n>       min-width: 100%;\n>       margin-left: auto;\n>       margin-right: auto;\n>     }\n>     & footer {\n>       margin-left: 0;\n>     }  \n>   }\n> }\n> ```\n\n## Making a Second Table of Contents Component\n\n[hack: TableOfContents2 additions · fanteastick/quartz-test@7a482cf · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/fanteastick/quartz-test/commit/7a482cfe7772142f6a6037d81e1ca44ef971a83b#diff-8a7a3a35709b33dd90a3a46deb08d6326bc17606dd172bfd8eaf82af52faa0f1","line":1937},{"title":"Don’t repeat yourself - Wikipedia![Wikipedia","target":"https://quartz.eilleeenz.com/static/favicons/wikipedia.avif","line":2045},{"title":"uicolors.app/create","target":"https://uicolors.app/","line":2200},{"title":"Sparkle Emoji for Bio","target":"https://www.aestheticbio.net/p/sparkle.html","line":2252},{"title":"add github source component · abhiaagarwal/notes@0649b06 · GitHub","target":"https://github.com/abhiaagarwal/notes/commit/0649b0645f505990908ca060af75cff6af006c3f","line":2321},{"title":"Git History","target":"https://githistory.xyz/","line":2327}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
